snippet.textDisplay:
Maithili was great and so was the arrangement, I just wish the rap added more to the spirit of Holi lyrically, words have been added just for the sake of rhymes, and some of it just makes no sense. 
No point adding rap, just for the sake of it. A fusion is supposed to help the music rise above the individual genres, this only brings it down.
Did great injustice to this song, and the work of other artists.
